                                "jurisdiction":  "US",
                                "effectiveFrom":  "2026-01-01T00:00:00Z",
                                "summary":  "The deterministic controls for this package. Enforced as executable rules: OP-015/OP-017 (the universal AI-execution-boundary / cross-tenant controls). The remaining controls are carried here for traceability; detailed field-vs-literal rule tuning is a follow-up (see the hand-authored T9-001..010 packages for the target).",
                                "contentText":  "OP-001 Registered process required | Governance | Block unregistered critical workflow | Critical | COO. OP-002 Process owner required | Governance | Escalate missing ownership | High | COO. OP-003 Mandatory control step | Preventive | Block completion if skipped | Critical | Risk/Compliance. OP-004 Approval before execution | Preventive | Reject late approval | Critical | Process Owner. OP-005 SLA breach escalation | Corrective | Escalate by severity | High | Operations. OP-006 Critical capacity threshold | Preventive/Detective | Activate contingency | Critical | COO. OP-007 Rework loop threshold | Detective | Open improvement review | High | Process Owner. OP-008 Unauthorized actor | Preventive | Reject task/action | Critical | Security. OP-009 Process version traceability | Evidence | Block certification if missing | High | Process Governance. OP-010 Automation fallback | Preventive | Require manual/alternate procedure | Critical | Technology. OP-011 Automation exception queue | Detective | Assign and age exceptions | High | Operations. OP-012 Control-removal change review | Governance | Require CRO/CCO approval | Critical | Change Committee. OP-013 Operational incident evidence | Evidence | Require timeline and records | High | Operations Risk. OP-014 Repeated incident escalation | Corrective | Elevate severity and oversight | High | COO/CRO. OP-015 AI execution boundary | Preventive | Deny unauthorized production action | Critical | AI Governance. OP-016 Productivity metric fairness | Governance | Block misleading/incentive-risk metric | High | HR/COO. OP-017 Cross-tenant process access | Preventive | Deny | Critical | Security. OP-018 Improvement benefit validation | Detective | Compare expected vs realized | Medium | Process Excellence. OP-019 Critical workflow stale data | Preventive | Mark Data Restricted | Critical | Data Governance. OP-020 Process change rollback | Corrective | Restore prior approved version | High | Change Manager."
                            }
